  <brief_title>Digital Sizing for Orthopaedic Hip Implants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Photo-manipulation of Digital Radiographs and Digitized Templates as a Method for Preoperative Sizing of Total Hip Arthroplasties</official_title>
  <sponsors>
